上係點，係人都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T05:56:12.000Z","msg":"成日講一國兩制不變形、不走樣,但又要不斷破壞一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"569e3449b9dff86480d1be69675b2684bb474206","tid":1790554,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"外國勢力邊有咁得閒理澳門<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d89457c3545b1e011863af59abbd79d1ac124f","tid":1790554,"uid":318557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T05:59:06.000Z","msg":"澳門一國一制唔駛理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7974e0fd3934649ec08dbf96eaa07ef0801e0cb7","tid":1790554,"uid":146285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4ad0cc37333164b31acbec29b5bc71cc1a12c5f3","tid":1790554,"uid":282637,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b24097d0586365ada83f7318adeb30724127dd18","tid":1790554,"uid":129169,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T05:47:10.000Z","msg":"講就講得好聽，實際上係點，係人都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T05:56:12.000Z","msg":"成日講一國兩制不變形、不走樣,但又要不斷破壞一國兩制<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:01:10.000Z","msg":"一國兩制不變(中共心中的)形、不走(中共心中的)樣"},{"pid":"3cead37cb4fc720cdad3bdc105d4a4c1beb9d2a0","tid":1790554,"uid":59283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:03:38.000Z","msg":"法案已立理撚得你"},{"pid":"9011aabd9124261b607d2499619a9bfefaa409f1","tid":1790554,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T06:04:06.000Z","msg":"香港金總就極權無理打壓抗爭支援之譴責聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1790265\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1790265</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aed6d7a0064544a353349d4600bc7decca5faa98","tid":1790554,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislik